metadata.name: Civies by VotingSmarter - Georgy
metadata.description: This is the first official drop by the civic tech startup VotingSmarter. Meet Georgy! He is the first in a series of change makers from history known as The Civies, who are here to fund technology that gives everyone the political access & influence that is currently only available to corporations and the super-rich. Each of these 17,760 pfps symbolize political freedom and will be a key for upcoming VotingSmarter technologies.
